109\r\n\r\nonly if we move it down to the actual storage back-end we can used the best solution for every back-end, like the php mkdir option \"recursive\"\r\n\r\n@icewind1991 i'm not sure what you want to put in the common storage back-end? the function \"mkdir\" is already there. it just needs to be implemented for each storage backen-end in the appropriate way. this patch provides it for the local back-end. other back-ends can / have to follow."},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/11569539","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/pull/958#issuecomment-11569539","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/958","id":11569539,"user":{"login":"icewind1991","id":1283854,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/7c20f90ca5df67dd2cad22a8e2f80d8f?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2fc818423776eba38604496a7caddc0251.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"7c20f90ca5df67dd2cad22a8e2f80d8f","url":"https://api.github.com/users/icewind1991","html_url":"https://github.com/icewind1991","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/icewind1991/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/icewind1991/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/icewind1991/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/icewind1991/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/icewind1991/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/icewind1991/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/icewind1991/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/icewind1991/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/icewind1991/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2012-12-20t11:04:03z","updated_at":"2012-12-20t11:04:03z","body":"having inconsistent behaviour behaviour between storage backends would be a bad thing. by adding a genetic implementation to the common we can prevent that.\n\nbjã¶rn schieãÿle <notifications@